The paper proposes a novel approach for Partial Label Learning (PLL) which is a subfield of machine learning. The method involves integrating different loss functions and regularization techniques to improve the learning model. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning) followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) since the proposed method can be applied to image classification tasks. Additionally, the paper mentions experiments on text data, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
